
 * when input [pageSize] changes in the parent component then this method will be called.
 We can invoke additional logic using it. To access an input variable it is good to create seperate get() method.
 - @Input() set pageSize(val: number) {
       this._pageSize = val;
       this.recalcLayout();
     }

     get pageSize(): number {
       return this._pageSize;
     }